					<h4>
						How it started
					</h4>
					<p>This is actually something I have been thinking about for many years.  I grew up close to a slave trading castle in Ghana where a quotation from the bible is inscribed on the wall of a room close to where the slaves were kept.  The fact that religions can co-exist with bad ideas has troubled me for a long time.
When I turned up for the Tech Crunch hackathon I thought on the spur of the moment that maybe this is my chance to do something about this problem I have pondered for many years.  Call it divine inspiration if you will ;)</p>
